features: Anti Loss Dog Tracker: the dog locator device can help to locate the item quickly and precisely after connecting to your mobile phone; Just press the button and follow the beeps, and it can locate diverse items like keys, wallets, TV remote controls, keychains, glasses, dog collars or other things within 15m/ 49.21 ft

Long Lasting Battery: the pet GPS tracking device for dogs is powered by CR2032 battery, which can last over 10 months; After running out of power, just need to replace the battery, low power consumption; Made of ABS material, it is sturdy and reliable to use, not easy to break

Alarm Reminder: in connection state, the phone and the key loss tracker will alarm at the same time when the locator device exceeds the preset range, and you can check the position on the map while they are disconnected.

Bidirectional Item Locating: by clicking on the cell phone app, the smart mobile tracking finder tags will sound an alarm, and by double clicking on the button of the anti loss device, the phone will automatically sound as well, so that you can easily find your lost items

Practical Gift: when you're scrambling to find your items, this GPS tracking tag will be helpful; This key finder is a good present for your family, elderly parents, and forgetful friends, it will definitely make them feel warm
body.description: Features: The mini pet tracking device can be applied as a nice helper when you have trouble finding your items, helping locate quickly. The mini tracking devices for dogs can be put in the bag, luggage, pets' collars, or wallet, etc., useful gifts for your families, elderly parents, pets and so on. Specifications: Material: ABS Color: black, silver Size: approx. 38 x 38 x 7 mm/ 1.5 x 1.5 x 0.28 inches Battery: CR2032 button battery Wireless distance: 15-20 meters Package includes: 10 x Mini dog tracking device 10 x Key rings Notes: Manual measurement, please allow slight errors on size. The color may exist a slight difference due to different screen displays. Small items are included, please keep away from children, to avoid swallowing.
